<view class="page-shell">
  <app-navbar title="代办授权" />

  <view class="page-body">
    <view class="page-note">
      代办授权适合给家属、共有人或代理人开放有限的办理权限，例如缴费、访客预约、查看账单等。
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view wx:for="{{records}}" wx:key="title" class="record-card">
        <view class="record-row">
          <view>
            <view class="icon-inline-row">
              <t-icon name="user" size="32rpx" class="ui-icon" />
              <view class="record-title">{{item.title}}</view>
            </view>
            <view class="record-note">{{item.note}}</view>
          </view>
          <t-tag theme="{{item.status === '已授权' ? 'success' : 'warning'}}" variant="light">{{item.status}}</t-tag>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section action-row">
      <button class="primary-button">新增授权</button>
      <button class="secondary-button">查看历史</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
